text: Divine Intervention () is a 2002 Palestinian Moroccan French German black comedy movie directed by Elia Suleiman (who also stars) and also starring Menashe Noy, Manal Khader, Denis Sandler Sapoznikov. ==Other websites== * * Category:2002 comedy movies Category:2000s black comedy movies Category:Palestinian movies Category:Moroccan movies Category:French comedy movies Category:German comedy movies Category:Movies directed by Elia Suleiman
